Aroma Wax Melts - Lavender & Rosemary

Ease into calm with the soothing blend of Lavender and Rosemary essential oils. Just one or two wax hearts in your burner fills the room with a clean, herbal aroma that clears the mind and helps unwind the day. The jar contains around 14 to 16 wax hearts (approx. 85g), ready to scent your space naturally.

Made from soy wax and infused with pure essential oils, these melts offer a gentle yet lasting fragrance experience. Lavender brings deep relaxation, while rosemary adds focus and freshness - perfect for peaceful evenings or mindful routines. Presented in a simple glass jar with a rustic heart tag, they make an eco-friendly, giftable treat for aromatherapy lovers.

Nutmeg brings a cosy, grounding depth, while lemon adds a crisp, uplifting note - perfect for mornings or moments of refreshment. Beautifully presented in a reusable glass jar, theyre ideal for gifting or enhancing your homes natural scent.

Large Botanical Garden - Japaneese Garden

AWGifts Dropship Europe Botanical Candle are made with soybean wax, which is a renewable resource and 3% fragrance oil. It will burn longer than most paraffin wax candle and with a clean almost smokeless flame. 

Botanical Candle are presented in round ceramic jars that can be reused,  bar-coded and packaged nicely in a presentation box. Each candle contains a wooden wick instead of a traditional wick

Notice: Never Leave a burning candle unattended. Burn candle out of reach of children and pets. Always leave at least 10cm between burning candle. Do not burn candle on or near anything that can catch fire.

Size: Diameter 8cm, Height 7.5cm, Weight 430g

Burning Time 30 hours

Sensual: Ylang Ylang Essential Oils + Coconut Oil


Mineral, rich Himalayan salt infused with 100% essential oils, Coconut Oil and Dry Rose Petals.


The healing powers of salt baths are still valued to the present day thanks to well-documented health benefits by ancient Greeks. And when choosing a salt to soak in, the pure Himalayan variety reigns supreme!

Because Himalayan salt is so rich in minerals.. to be exact 84 minerals.. soaking in salt water, soothe and repair damaged skin and promote cell renewal. And with the extra bit of Olive, Jojoba, Evening Primrose and other base oils, nourish and moisturise the skin.

However, we haven't stopped there and added plenty of pure essential oils and dry flowers to create that ultimate aromatherapy bathing experience.

Unit Name: Bath Salts in Vials - Gift Pack of 7
Webpage description (html):
Seeking an opulent item to diversify your offerings? Bath Salts in Vials – Gift Pack of 7 presents an ideal means to elevate your patrons’ bathing rituals. This thoughtfully selected gift collection features seven unique concoctions, tailored for each day of the week, enabling your customers to craft a spa-like ambiance within the confines of their own abode. .

The seven scents in this gift pack are:

Sensual:  Immerse yourself in the alluring combination of floral and sweet fragrances, allowing your concerns to dissolve into bliss. 

Relax: De-stress after a tiring day with the tranquil fragrance of lavender. 

Harmony: Attain a sense of proportion and tranquility with this inspiring amalgamation of tangy and piquant fragrances. 

Energise: Elevate your vitality and enliven your senses with this rejuvenating combination of citrus, ginger, and other invigorating fragrances. 

Detox: Purify and detoxify your body with this combination of sea salt, evening primrose, and other cleansing elements. 

Clarity: Revitalize your mind and concentrate your thoughts with this invigorating mix of salvia, rosemary, and other rejuvenating scents. 

Skin Revive: Renew and invigorate your skin with this combination of sea salt, vitamin E, and other nourishing components. 

Each vial contains enough bath salts for a single use, making them perfect for on-the-go or for those who like to switch up their scents frequently. The gift pack also makes a great gift for loved ones or for yourself.

Each pack includes 7x 40 grams of bath salts.

Unit Name: Chakra Bath Salt - Gift Pack of 7
Webpage description (html):
Unlock the potential of self-discovery with our exquisite collection of aromatherapy Chakra Bath Salt Vials, meticulously crafted to balance and harmonize the body's energy centers. 

This unique collection includes seven distinct bath salts, each specially formulated for a specific chakra, using premium essential oils.

  • Crown Chakra Bath Salt: Revitalize your Crown Chakra with the invigorating fusion of peppermint essential oil.  
  • Third Eye Chakra Bath Salt: Attain tranquility and inner peace with the soothing scent of lavender essential oil.
  • Throat Chakra Bath Salt: Enhance clear communication with the refreshing blend of eucalyptus and lemon essential oils. 
  • Heart Chakra Bath Salt: Foster love and compassion with the harmonious combination of chamomile and grapefruit essential oils. 
  • Solar Plexus Chakra Bath Salt: Achieve inner harmony and alleviate stress with the powerful essence of Ylang Ylang essential oil. 
  • Sacral Chakra Bath Salt: Awaken your creative spirit with the vibrant mix of sweet orange and cinnamon essential oils. 
  • Root Chakra Bath Salt: Gain strength and stability with the grounding blend of bergamot and spearmint essential oils.  

Ingredients: 

CROWN CHAKRA: Maris Sal, Mentha Piperita Oil, CI 18050, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Aqua, CI 45430, CI 42090, Limonene

THIRD EYE CHAKRA: SMaris Sal, Lavandula Angustifolia Oil, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Aqua, CI 42090, Linalool, Limonene

THROAT CHAKRA: Maris Sal, Citrus Limon Peel Oil, Eucalyptus Globulus Leaf Oil, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Aqua, CI 42090, Limonene, Citral

HEART CHAKRA: Maris Sal, CI 19140, Citrus Paradisi Peel Oil, Anthemis Nobilis Flower Oil, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Aqua, CI 42090, Limonene

SOLAR PLEXUS CHAKRA: Maris Sal, Cananga Odorata Flower Oil, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Aqua, CI 19140, Benzyl Salicylate, Farnesol

SACRAL CHAKRA: Maris Sal, Citrus Sinensis Peel Oil, Citrus Limon Peel Oil, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Aqua, CI 19140, CI 15985, Limonene, Linalool, Eugenol, Citral

ROOT CHAKRA: Maris Sal, CI 18050, Citrus Bergamia Fruit Oil, CI 19140, Mentha Spicata Herb Oil, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Aqua, CI 45430, Limonene, Linalool
